'''EAC-C2C'''是一组连通东亚地区国家的海底光缆网络，分别由EAC（东亚海底光缆系统，{{lang|en|East Asia Crossing}}）及C2C（城市到城市间海底光缆，{{lang|en|City-to-City Cable System}}）两个电缆网络合并组成。<ref>{{cite web |author=September 14, 2007 |url=http://www.telecomasia.net/content/asia-netcom-merges-eac-c2c-0 |title=Asia Netcom merges EAC with C2C |publisher=Telecom Asia |date=2007-09-14 |accessdate=2014-06-28 |archive-date=2015-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707203700/http://www.telecomasia.net/content/asia-netcom-merges-eac-c2c-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>由Asia Netcom完成网络，现该公司合并入{{tsl|en|Pacnet}}并交由新公司管理。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.optoiq.com/index/display/article-display/358680/articles/lightwave/news-amp-analysis/pacnet-upgrades-capacity-on-eac-c2c.html |title=Laser Focus World: Lasers, Photonics, Optics News and Laser Technology Advances |publisher=Optoiq.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-28 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年10月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

